{"name":"eclipse","slug":"eclipse","count":1,"postlist":[{"title":"修改Eclipse中中文的字体大小","slug":"修改Eclipse中中文的字体大小","date":"2018-12-11T10:00:59.000Z","updated":"2018-12-11T10:00:59.339Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/修改Eclipse中中文的字体大小.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>首先进入到eclipse的安装目录下面:</p>\n<p>然后找到/plugins/org.eclipse.jface_*.jar</p>\n<p>使用rar打开这个Jar文件进入到目录:/org/eclipse/jface/resources</p>\n<p>找到你当前系统所属的属性文件,如Win8系统的则是:jfacefonts_windows8.properties</p>\n<p>然后使用文本编辑器打开并修改里面的字体大小(后面是字体的像素)<br><figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">org.eclipse.jface.bannerfont.0=Segoe UI-bold-12</span><br><span class=\"line\">org.eclipse.jface.bannerfont.1=Tahoma-bold-12</span><br><span class=\"line\"> </span><br><span class=\"line\">org.eclipse.jface.headerfont.0=Segoe UI-bold-14</span><br><span class=\"line\">org.eclipse.jface.headerfont.1=Tahoma-bold-14</span><br><span class=\"line\"> </span><br><span class=\"line\">org.eclipse.jface.textfont.0=Consolas-regular-12</span><br><span class=\"line\">org.eclipse.jface.textfont.1=Courier New-regular-12</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n","text":"首先进入到eclipse的安装目录下面:然后找到/plugins/org.eclipse.jface_*.jar使用rar打开这个Jar文件进入到目录:/org/eclipse/jface/resources找到你当前系统所属的属性文件,如Win8系统的则是:jfacefonts","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[{"name":"eclipse","slug":"eclipse","count":1,"path":"api/categories/eclipse.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"eclipse","slug":"eclipse","count":1,"path":"api/tags/eclipse.json"},{"name":"font-size","slug":"font-size","count":1,"path":"api/tags/font-size.json"}]}]}